1.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、监管机关或其他有权机关所要求的披露；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3、在紧急情形下为维护您的利益所进行的披露。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">信息的使用</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">为提升和改善我们的服务，我们或者从我们取得您个人信息的任何人士可能会将您的个人信息用作以下用途：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1、向您提供我们的产品或服务；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2、向您推介我们的产品或服务；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3、法律或者契约所要求的披露；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4、为您设计相关的产品或服务；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5、与产品或服务相关的调研、访问；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6、您所请求的特定行为；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7、与上述有关的其他用途。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">在我们将您的个人信息用于我们产品或服务的直接促销之用途时，我们将为您提供拒绝该等促销服务的机会。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">在使用您的个人信息进行以上之用途时，我们可能会将您的个人信息提供给对我们承担保密义务的以下人士：会计师、律师、承包商、服务供应商、合作伙伴、关联机构等。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;">IP信息与Cookies</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">当您浏览我们的网站时，我们可能会收集一些与您的个人隐私信息无关的信息，包括</font>IP地址、访问时间、浏览器类型等。这些信息将用于网站管理，行为跟踪以及提高网站的服务质量。这些和个人隐私无关的信息可能会分享给第三方公司，进而为我们的注册人员提供更多相关的服务。记录用户的IP地址也是出于安全和监控的目的。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">在您浏览我们的网站时，我们会用</font>cookies来储存您的偏好以及记录session信息，作用包括确保您不会重复收到相同内容的通知，根据浏览器和用户配置的不同定制网页内容及显示方式。我们不会将储存在cookies里的信息关联到任何与用户身份有关的个人资料。您可以通过设置浏览器的选项来限制部分或所有cookies的接收，但这可能会影响您使用我们网站所提供的部分服务。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">外部链接</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">我们网站包含一些外部网站的链接。我们对这些网站的隐私管理和行为不承担责任。当跳转到外部网站时，用户请阅读该网站的隐私政策。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">查询与修改</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">为保护您的隐私和安全，在采取合理的验证措施后，我们允许您查阅或修改您的个人信息。就个人信息的修改，部分个人信息的修改是您自己可以在我们的网站上自行完成的；另一些个人信息的修改，您必须通知我们，并向我们提供相关的证明文件。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">法律适用与争议解决</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">本隐私声明适用中华人民共和国法律并依照其解释。因本隐私声明所生之争议，应友好协商解决；如果协商无法解决，任何一方应将争议提交</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">本财政单位所在地</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">仲裁委员会按照其届时有效的仲裁规则进行仲裁，仲裁地点</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">为本财政单位所在地。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">解释与修改</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">本声明的解释权归</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">本财政单位</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">所有。若我们决定更改我们的隐私权声明，我们将会把所做的变更放在我们的网站上，如此您就会注意到在何种情况下我们收集数据以及如何使用此数据。若我们决定在任何时间点上以不同于数据收集当时之声明中的方式使用个人基本数据，我们将用</font>E-mail的方式或其他方式通知我们的客户。客户将有选择是否让我们以不同的方式使用其数据的权利，我们也将根据资料收集当时的隐私权政策中所规范的方式使用信息。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.5000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">与我们联系</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">如果您有与隐私保护、网站操作有关的问题，请将意见或建议发送至我们的邮箱：</font></span><span><a href="mailto:service@bosssoft.com.cn"><u><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:11.5000pt;">service@</span></u><u><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:11.5000pt;">bosssoft</span></u><u><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:11.5000pt;">.com.cn</span></u></a></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">；或者与我们的客服联系，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">博思致新为您提供相关的服务技术支持，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">联系电话</font>010-83010910</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="微软雅黑">。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(102,102,102);font-size:11.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" align="right" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:right;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p></div>`,
    };
